{"tid":839713,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【復興北海道】6.7級地震後推復興劵 10月起外國旅客住宿打三折","createTime":"2018-09-28T06:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T18:58:42.000Z","uid":65328,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e52d9a4e396e396ae36feae0bf733e897e585c39","tid":839713,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"日本北海道在本月6日經歷6.7級大地震，當地政府為復興經濟，特推出旅行住宿津貼。外國遊客每晚可獲七成補貼，等同住宿費用打三折，最多能補助五晚。優惠以每一晚補助20,000日圓為上限，即港幣1,380元。"},{"pid":"91fb36a4b9e184d2dd4d2bdef8003250de306cbe","tid":839713,"uid":150204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"已經比左錢個D計唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee47e4ae2a06fd0a3477ec061c47fd65d43a1918","tid":839713,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"ed9cc6e1603762f16d8377e3b4b36e970141c01d","tid":839713,"uid":139270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T08:45:04.000Z","msg":"有無詳細呢 我都比左錢"},{"pid":"9351617ce9c956953bdaaa5f8abf865086429014","tid":839713,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"真定假啊???<br />\n我12月去啊~咩錢都未比啊~"},{"pid":"989d8529b7bc5e936c3eec6dff5a864cd91c1ad9","tid":839713,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:17:37.000Z","msg":"剩係搵到tw source"},{"pid":"51bddd8a3fcfd2a3f2c3a8f70a880a33ac29221b","tid":839713,"uid":39369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:17:46.000Z","msg":"屌阿？ 我取消哂先見到"},{"pid":"45ab18abbc795dc8718562b0a54850f6e1fcc04b","tid":839713,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T09:25:38.000Z","msg":"上東橫inn睇都唔見有平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1948e508cfd5c7c9e3a4a57ceefcdce15581557b","tid":839713,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":